n efficient mechanism to release\na significant amount of gas-phase H2CO into the Horsehead PDR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2011 16:03:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2011 09:22:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
